====Usage notes====
Despite the technically-correct radical being {{l|zh|⺼||meat|tr=-}} as described in this entry’s [[#Glyph_origin|glyph origin]] section, {{lang|zh|有}} is associated with the radical {{l|zh|月||moon|tr=-}} in dictionaries for historical reasons and is likewise written as if it contained the {{lang|zh|月}} radical, i.e. it has {{l|zh|二|tr=-}} instead of {{l|zh|冫|tr=-}} inside of {{l|zh|冂|tr=-}}.

