# {{senseid|zh|there is}} [[there is]]; to [[exist]] {{gl|when a subject is absent}}
#: {{zh-x|有 很 多 人。|'''There are''' a lot of people.}}
#: {{zh-x|這兒{r} 有 書 嗎？|'''Are there''' any books here?}}
#: {{zh-x|這裡 有-著[着]{zhe} 清新 的 空氣。|'''There is''' fresh air here.}}
#: {{zh-x|「^陳 ^小明 同學！」「^有！」|"Is [[John Doe]] here?" "'''Present'''!" ''(scene of [[take roll|taking roll]] at a classroom)''}}
