#: {{zh-x|這 條 繩子 有 兩 米 長。|This rope is two meters long.}}
#: {{zh-x|有 這麼 貴 嗎？|Is it really that expensive?}}
# {{lb|zh|euphemistic}} to be [[pregnant]] with a child
# [[abundant]]; [[affluent]]
